name: E1M8, Phobos Anomaly Revisited
description: This is my way of seing the map 8 of the first episode of Ultimate doom, phobos anomaly. This level, like you've guessed, replaces the e1m8 of ultimate doom and features monsters from the realm667 site, textures from various sources(some from kdizd,zpack and alot from the nb5d1.wad), scripting, etc...
